# SPECTRAL PCM ŌĆö Brand & Design System

## Brand Identity
Dark, technical, premium military aesthetic. **Flight-deck adjacent. Contractor-grade. Signals expertise without ostentation.**

Deliberately avoids:
- "Cartoon military" (camo patterns, AK silhouettes, exploding fonts)
- "Corporate defence prime" (bland sans-serif, generic stock photography)
- "Silicon Valley defence-tech" (oversaturated neon, glitch effects, AI hype)

Target feel: **Block-Time / MOC (Mission Operations Centre) / professional cockpit** ŌĆö a system a real military operator finds credible.

